Very simple at the moment. Needs serious work on the rotational stuff.

Requires a mysql copy of the Static Data Export from Eve Online, along with PHP with PDO embedded in it. Also requires a copy of Three.js from https://github.com/mrdoob/three.js/tree/master/build in the same directory

Check out the code, rename db.inc.php.example to db.inc.php, edit the connection details, edit the url variable to point at your own version, then open the page in a browser. click on the grey planets to go to a new constellation.


